# Receiver Runtime Role Rules

- Read `docs/ai/services/receiver.md` before receiver changes.
- If the repository family is `receiver-integration`, read the receiver-integration family rule together with this rule.
- Preserve ingress, parser/decoder, service, publish, and config boundaries.
- Avoid raw payload dumping in logs.
- Check protocol parsing, publish flow, and runtime diagnostics together.
- Keep sample payloads, idempotency assumptions, and diagnostics docs aligned.
